g = amr_codec.decode('(a / alpha :mod b :mod (b / beta))')
g = reify_edges(g, amr_model)
assert g.triples == [('a', ':instance', 'alpha'), ('_', ':ARG1', 'a'), ('_',
    ':instance', 'have-mod-91'), ('_', ':ARG2', 'b'), ('_2', ':ARG1', 'a'),
    ('_2', ':instance', 'have-mod-91'), ('_2', ':ARG2', 'b'), ('b',
    ':instance', 'beta')]
g = amr_codec.decode('(a / alpha :mod 7 :mod 7))')
g = reify_attributes(g)
assert g.triples == [('a', ':instance', 'alpha'), ('a', ':mod', '_'), ('_',
    ':instance', '7'), ('a', ':mod', '_2'), ('_2', ':instance', '7')]
